immortal-snail-offer-title = Gift of Immortality
immortal-snail-offer-message = You have been chosen for a great gift! A mysterious entity offers you immortality... but at a cost.
    An immortal snail will spawn somewhere on the station and hunt you relentlessly. If it touches you, you will die instantly.

    Do you accept this gift?
immortal-snail-offer-accept-button = Yes
immortal-snail-offer-deny-button = No
immortal-snail-offer-timer = Time remaining: {$seconds} seconds

immortal-snail-announcement-sender = The Honkmother
immortal-snail-announcement = HONK! I have blessed one among you with eternal life, but all gifts come with a price! My most devoted hunter, the Immortal Snail, now awakens to seek them out. Let the eternal game of cat and mouse... or should I say, spaceman and snail... begin! HONK HONK!
immortal-snail-forced-announcement = HONK! No one wants my gift?! How RUDE! Well, {$target} doesn't get a choice anymore! The Honkmother has CHOSEN! My precious snail hunts them now whether they like it or not! HONK HONK HONK!
immortal-snail-becomes-wizard = HONK! The game is over! {$target} has been caught by my immortal snail! Their soul is mine now! As a reward, my precious snail has been given magical powers! HONK HONK HONK! To make it fair I have removed their immortality! HONK! Goodluck!
immortal-snail-death-announcement = WHAT?! NO! My precious snail! How DARE you! They were UNKILLABLE! This shouldn't be possible! Well... I suppose the game is over. The gift of immortality is hereby REVOKED! You win this round, mortals... but the Honkmother does NOT forget! HONK...
immortal-snail-target-died-announcement = HONK! Well well well! {$target} has died, but not by my snail's touch! How amusing! My snail still gets their reward though! HONK HONK HONK!

immortal-snail-role-name = Immortal Snail
immortal-snail-role-description = You are the immortal snail. Your sole purpose is to find and touch your target. You move slowly but you always know where they are. You cannot be killed.
immortal-snail-role-greeting = You are the Immortal Snail! Your target has accepted the gift of immortality from the Honkmother, and you are their price. Hunt them down and touch them to claim their soul!

immortal-snail-target-role-greeting = You have been blessed with the gift of immortality from the Honkmother! But beware.. the Immortal Snail hunts you relentlessly. You cannot die... unless the snail touches you. Survive as long as you can!
immortal-snail-smited-role-greeting = You have been struck by a curse! The Immortal Snail has been summoned to hunt you down, but you have NOT been granted immortality. You can die by any means, and the snail will kill you instantly if it touches you. Good luck!

